"{\n  \"text\": \"Hi everybody, I'm looking to become a market gardener this season, and I am doing so because I have a better gardening technique than you can find at the supermarkets. This is compost that I make myself. It is well broken down material that is then cured, and that is applied to my garden as the only amendment, and I do it regularly. This provides food for the biology of the soil. I do not add salts, I do not add poisons, I do not need to. And this makes healthy, vibrant living food full of the biomes that make up healthy living. Those feed your biomes. This is what's going wrong with our lives and our world and our culture. We need to restore our biomes because this is the basis of our health, and our health is breaking down right at the moment when our environment is becoming more and more toxic and a runaway roller coaster. Scotty's Fermented Foods is also my side business. Thanks, y'all.\",\n  \"sentences\": [\n    {\n      \"text\": \" Hi everybody, I'm looking to become a market gardener this season, and I am doing so because I have a better gardening technique than you can find at the supermarkets.\",\n      \"start\": 0.24,\n      \"end\": 10.16,\n      \"duration\": 9.92,\n      \"confidence\": 0.996,\n      \"tokens\": [\n        {\n          \"text\": \" Hi\",\n          \"start\": 0.24,\n          \"end\": 0.48,\n          \"duration\": 0.24,\n          \"confidence\": 0.996\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" ever\",\n          \"start\": 0.56,\n          \"end\": 0.72,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"yb\",\n          \"start\": 0.72,\n          \"end\": 0.88,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"ody\",\n          \"start\": 0.88,\n          \"end\": 1.04,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \",\",\n          \"s